extends layout

block mainContent
  #topleftdiv
  #about
    | <span class=orbitron> RADIOCASE </span> -  a database for radiological cases
    br
    br
    ul 
      li Do you have that creeping feeling that your collected cases will disappear in the next PACS upgrade?
      li Would you like to be able to access your cases from anywhere/anything with an internet connection (including your nice, shiny iPad)?
      li Do you like sharing?
    br
    p
      | - Just use <span class=orbitron> RADIOCASE </span>
    hr
    br
    h5
      | Cheat-sheet
    table#cheatsheet
      tr
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/question.png') 
        td Markdown help
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/box.png')
        td Metadata / Categorize
      tr
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/plus.png')
        td Add page / image 
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/minus.png')
        td Delete page / case
      tr
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/eye.png')
        td Case visible
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/eye-prohibition.png')
        td Case hidden
      tr
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/arrow-090.png')
        td Move image up
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/arrow-270.png')
        td Move image down
      tr
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/disc.png') 
        td Save page
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/cross.png')
        td Remove image
      tr
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/pencil.png')
        td Edit page / text
        td  
          img(src='/static/ico/tick.png')
        td Done
      tr
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/arrow-180.png')
        td Previous page
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/arrow.png') 
        td Next page
      tr
        td 
          img(src='/static/ico/star.png')
        td Favorite
        td
          img(src='/static/ico/balloon.png')
        td Feedback
    br
    hr
    br
    ul
      li To filter and only show your favorites type #fav into the box at the case list. 
      li Type your username into the box to filter and only show your cases.
      li Type #se for Swedish cases, #es for Spanish and #gb for English.
    br
    br
    | Please see 
    a(href="/stat/colophon") colophon
    |  for the techical stuff and 
    a(href="/stat/disclaimer") disclaimer
    |  for the rest.
